txt.en: Zarhal Kôz can be found somewhere within Uya Hujûm.\n\nYou have arrived in Uya Hujûm and should now battle through the encampment until you find Zarhal Kôz.
Jarl Gurthilm is standing with his men in Uya Hujûm.\n\nYou have come with the Variags to Uya Hujûm and should now speak to Jarl Gurthilm.
Zarhal Kôz's men leap forth from the tent!
Defeat Zarhal Kôz and his men
Zarhal Kôz can be found deep within Uya Hujûm.\n\nZarhal Kôz has called forth his men and now attacks. You should defeat him.
Zarhal Kôz can be found deep within Uya Hujûm.\n\nYou have discovered Zarhal Kôz's whereabouts and should now confront him with the Variags.
Zarhal Kôz lies slain amidst his wealth of gold and treasures!
Jarl Gurthilm and his company have travelled to the stronghold of Uya Hujûm to deal their vengeance upon Zarhal Kôz and the Khundolar.
A great tent stands before you... and you can hear hasty chatter within!
'The day is won, [placeholder]. Let us begone from this place!'
Fight your way through Uya Hujûm and find Zarhal Kôz

'Are you prepared, [placeholder]?

'The blades of my men have tasted much of the blood of the Khundolar, but our foe eludes us still. A coward to the last, I do not doubt!

'We shall press onward into the mountainside... and soon there shall be nowhere left for him to hide!

'Ready your arms and let us go.'
